'''羅伯特·勞森伯格'''（{{lang-en|Robert Rauschenberg}}，{{bd|1925年|10月22日|2008年|5月12日}}），[[美國|美國]][[畫家|畫家]]、圖形藝術家。

==生平==
他的早期作品屬於[[波普藝術|波普藝術]]運動。羅伯特·勞森伯格以1950年代的“組合”而聞名於世，該作品使用非傳統材料及物體來創新組合。勞森伯格是一個畫家，也是一個[[雕塑家|雕塑家]]，他也創作攝影，版畫，[[造紙術|造紙術]]及表演<ref name="Retrospective">{{cite news
 |url         = http://www.csmonitor.com/durable/1997/11/28/feat/arts.1.html
 |title       = Rauschenberg's Signature on the Century
 |work        = [[Christian_Science_Monitor|Christian Science Monitor]]
 |date        = November 28, 1997
 |author      = Marlena Donohue
 |quote       = Rauschenberg's mammoth career [[retrospective|retrospective]] at the [[Solomon_R._Guggenheim_Museum|Solomon R. Guggenheim Museum]] (and other New York sites) from Sept. 19 to Jan. 7, 1998… along with longtime friends pre-[[Pop_Art|Pop]] painter [[Jasper_Johns|Jasper Johns]] and the late conceptual composer [[John_Cage|John Cage]], Rauschenberg pretty much defined the technical and philosophic art landscape and its offshoots after [[Abstract_Expressionism|Abstract Expressionism]].
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20060707213354/http://www.csmonitor.com/durable/1997/11/28/feat/arts.1.html
 |archivedate = 2006年7月7日
 |accessdate  = 2017年3月11日
}}</ref><ref name="AskArt">{{cite web |url= http://www.askart.com//AskART/R/robert_rauschenberg/robert_rauschenberg.aspx?searchtype=SUMMARY&artist=30093 |title= Robert Rauschenberg in "The Century's 25 Most Influential Artists" |work= [[ARTnews|ARTnews]], [http://artnews.com/issues/issue.asp?id=9805 May 1999] issue |quote= Born with the name Milton Rauschenberg in [[Port_Arthur,_Texas|Port Arthur, Texas]], Robert Rauschenberg became one of the major artists of his generation and is credited along with [[Jasper_Johns|Jasper Johns]] of breaking the stronghold of [[Abstract_Expressionism|Abstract Expressionism]]. Rauschenberg was known for [[Assemblage_(art)|assemblage]], [[Conceptualism|conceptualist]] methods, printmaking, and willingness to experiment with non-artistic materials—all innovations that anticipated later movements such as [[Pop_Art|Pop Art]], Conceptualism, and [[Minimalism|Minimalism]]. |access-date= 2017-03-11 |archive-date= 2014-08-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140829033440/http://www.askart.com/AskART/R/robert_rauschenberg/robert_rauschenberg.aspx?searchtype=SUMMARY&artist=30093 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。他於1993年獲得[[國家藝術勳章|國家藝術勳章]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nea.gov/honors/medals/medalists_year.html#93 |title=Lifetime Honors - National Medal of Arts |access-date=2017-09-20 |archive-date=2011-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721054307/http://www.nea.gov/honors/medals/medalists_year.html#93 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在1995年獲得[[達文西世界藝術獎|達文西世界藝術獎]]（Leonardo da Vinci World Award of Arts）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Leonardo da Vinci World Award of Arts 1995|url=http://www.consejoculturalmundial.org/winners-arts-robertrauschenberg.php|accessdate=August 14, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505022446/http://www.consejoculturalmundial.org/winners-arts-robertrauschenberg.php|archivedate=2014年5月5日}}</ref>
羅伯特·勞森伯格在[[紐約市|紐約市]]以及[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]Captiva Island生活，直到2008年5月12日因心臟衰竭去世。

